headline: EQT Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE: EQT) today announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.1575 per share, payable on March 3, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 18, 2025.
